{
  "stem": "19939.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 96.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the first thing, they came and when we had to give up all the furs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were so scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody was giving away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody somehow can I say something, what my husband told me that he read somewhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That let's say the Israelis, right, looked down at the survivors, that why didn't they resist, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why didn't they resist?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember, we were always the second-class citizens in Poland, always being put down, and-- and called names by the Poles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had no rights, let's say, in the universities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were sitting in the back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were not allowed to some universities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I know my husband's cousins and his father-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my husband's father had a PhD in chemistry before the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he studied in-- in Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had another-- his mother had a the cousin, a doctor, a surgeon who studied in Prague too, not in Poland, because they were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not in the character.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not possible, because I have to stress this fact that I just cannot get used to this violence here and the crime, and this something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were not well-- you know, there were no luxuries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no washing machines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what it was there, it was-- there was really no crime, maybe in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jews, nobody would-- you know, never heard of a Jew striking another one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This atmosphere--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first thing they came--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The furs, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- and slowly, let's say there was snow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So every family had to send a member of the family to shovel snow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember myself had to go and-- you know, they didn't have to-- this was Poland, right?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sidewalks-- it's a sidewalk, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
